              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "CYCLO"
                ],
                "institute": "1USATAM"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Experiment performed at K500",
                "superconducting cyclotron, which delivered primary",
                "beam of 12C. Secondary beam 12N was produced by (p,n)",
                "reaction on cryogenic H2 gas cell, operated at 2.2 atm.",
                "The resulting 12N beam was separated by the Momentum",
                "Achromat Recoil Spectrometer (MARS) and had a purity",
                "of around 99.8% and a rate of around 2E+5 particles/s."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Composite melamine target (C3H6N6) located at the",
                "final focal plane of MARS with of a thickness of",
                "1.58+-0.05 mg/cm2."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EDE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "SI",
                "SI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Four modular dE-E telescopes",
                "5 x 5 cm2 in area, placed 182 mm downstream",
                "from the melamine target.The front dE detectors were",
                "16-strip position-sensitive silicon detectors,",
                "110 mu-m thick, telescopes 1 and 2, and 65 mu-m thick,",
                "telescopes 3 and 4). The back E-residual detectors",
                "had the same area coverage and were all 500 mu-m",
                "thick."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "HISTORY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "date": 20090409,
                "history": "C"
              },
              "free_text": [
